330
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:58,250
I hope you can take action

331
00:16:58,250 --> 00:16:59,460
to rescue her.

332
00:17:06,110 --> 00:17:07,200
I've decided to save

333
00:17:07,850 --> 00:17:08,950
