395
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:17,110
I'll be there in a moment.

396
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:18,920
Jue,

397
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,760
let's go.

398
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,270
So, that is

399
00:19:27,270 --> 00:19:28,510
