434
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:42,150
Let's forget

435
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:43,590
the past and start anew.

436
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,030
Let bygones

437
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,510
