462
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,830
I have no regrets.

463
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,300
Come on.

464
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:38,400
Let's go to the Wei Mansion.

465
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:39,640
